Package: purpler
Title: Easy, Tidy Access to the PurpleAir API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Harrison", "DeFord", , "hdeford1@umbc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-5978-0422"))
Description: An interface to GET information from the PurpleAir API.
        'purpler' will return information from multiple sensors by bounding box, 
        or historical information about a single sensor.
URL: https://github.com/oonuttlet/purpler
